{"tid":970473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"假扮學生妹重溫校園夢？美32歲婦被捕","createTime":"2019-01-05T23:08:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T10:24:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"049047103858b3f2b684c9c80aa4a37169c6edcc","tid":970473,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T23:08:26.000Z","msg":"（北美通訊）不少人都懷念校園生活，美國一名32歲婦人謊稱自己是15歲無家少女，進高中上了一天課，引起家長關注校園安全。<br />\n事發於紐約州格林縣（Green County）開羅達勒姆校區（Cairo-Durham School District），32歲婦人古德里奇（Michaelann Goodrich）謊稱自己是15歲少女瑪迪遜（Riley Madison），試圖註冊成開羅達勒姆高中生。<br />\n當局表示，古德里奇上了一天課，在去年12月20日搭了校巴往返學校，翌日（即12月21日）缺席，之後學校便開始放寒假。古德里奇在12月28日被捕，被控一項提供虛假文書罪、偽造商業紀錄罪和非法闖入罪。<br />\n當局仍未查明古德里奇的犯案動機，不過他們發現她早已持有高中文憑。校區總監Anthony Taibi表示，根據「麥金尼-凡托無家可歸者援助法案」，由於古德里奇聲稱自己是無家者，他們必須立即讓她入學。<br />\n女兒在開羅達勒姆中學就讀的Joshua Mack表示擔憂，「這有點令人不安，她可能是任何一個人，你知道，你聽說過各種校園槍擊事件，可能是任何人進來試圖取得學校的建築設計圖。」當局呼籲與古德里奇接觸過的人，致電當地縣警辦公室報案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190105/large/1546668813_730c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190105%2Flarge%2F1546668813_730c.png&h=fe97991d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"799f8a4eb19efb5afbb1d0a6c5b2944fbaaf39a1","tid":970473,"uid":178842,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T23:11:09.000Z","msg":"個樣好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e480cafee1ad7f2212c409e3fbc06a4cb53abbbd","tid":970473,"uid":101968,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T23:12:13.000Z","msg":"樓主好波，無寫  32歲美婦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5be78700be471c7bf3a72ec8ab32acb529f4d5","tid":970473,"uid":66566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T23:42:03.000Z","msg":"咁似荷李活電影既情節既 結局應該係佢同班學生變到好friend 之後仲同個老師係埋一齊"},{"pid":"ea82f4c2ba67ba580e2ca16ba406cfa09c26be26","tid":970473,"uid":8171,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T23:43:00.000Z","msg":"肥屍大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b455cd618edeab74db7dcbceee2eee10a94c935a","tid":970473,"uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1f5be78700be471c7bf3a72ec8ab32acb529f4d5","tid":970473,"uid":66566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T23:42:03.000Z","msg":"咁似荷李活電影既情節既 結局應該係佢同班學生變到好friend 之後仲同個老師係埋一齊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T03:44:25.000Z","msg":"逃學威龍結局嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ee1367582773b4d6b08b5f49178bd5cffbf07e","tid":970473,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"799f8a4eb19efb5afbb1d0a6c5b2944fbaaf39a1","tid":970473,"uid":178842,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T23:11:09.000Z","msg":"個樣好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T10:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}